JFileSynchronizerTreeNode
public class FileSynchronizerTodoTaskTreeNode
extends FileSynchronizationStatusTreeNode

File Synchronizer Todo Status Tree Node object. This is a node that add the capability to flag a todo task depending on synchronization status. This implementation act by default as a backuper. (their is - by default - no modification of sources files and no deletion of destination files)

Author:
Pingus
